<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Grouplancer Email Activation Mail</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #FAFAFA;
            color: #222222;
        }

        p {
            margin: 1rem 1rem 1rem 1rem;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-weight: 550;
        }

        div {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgb(245, 193, 193), white);
            border: 2px solid rgb(105, 0, 0);
            width: 57%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div>
        <p>
        <p>Hi <%= user.name %>
        </p>
        <p>We received your request for a single-use code to use with your Gmail account.</p>
        <p>Your single-use code is: <%= activationCode %>
        </p>
        <p>If you didn't request this code, you can safely ignore this email. Someone else might have typed your email
            address by mistake.</p>
        <p>Thanks,</p>
        <p>The Grouplancer account team.</p>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>